org.mini2Dx.core.collision.util

Class StaticCollisionPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mini2Dx.gdx.math.Vector2
      • org.mini2Dx.core.geom.Point
        • org.mini2Dx.core.collision.util.StaticCollisionPoint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, CollisionObject, Positionable, Interpolatable, org.mini2Dx.gdx.math.Vector<org.mini2Dx.gdx.math.Vector2>, org.mini2Dx.gdx.utils.Disposable

    public class StaticCollisionPoint
extends Point
implements CollisionObject
    An implementation of a collision point that will not move between updates/frames, thus, does not register as an interpolating collision. Due to this, memory and CPU overhead are reduced compared to using the CollisionPoint implementation.
